<p>can anyone tell me how to edit it to add the icons ? </p> <p>As you told you are new so I am creating a listview similar to your needs. If you are still facing any problem then you can ask. There can be other methods also but I have followed below one.</p>
<p>I have created it in three steps:
1. Create a listview layout in XML.
2. Create a layout for your row which you will inflate and set on listview row.
3. Create a custom adapter by extending arrayadapter.
4. Setting custom adapter.</p>
<p>Step 1: Create a listview layout in XML.</p>
<p>Below given XML code will create a listview for you.</p>
<pre><code><RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
