Custom listview scrollin isn't smooth <p>I've created a custom listview which is working great apart from the fact that the list doesn't smooth scroll. Its choppy and slow.</p>
<p>Here's the code where I populate the listview:</p>
<pre><code>@Override
public View getView(int position, View convertView, ViewGroup parent) {
View v = convertView;
