<p>The <code>AdapterView.onItemClickListener</code> doesnt yield any errors but doesnt seem to function whatsoever.</p>
<p>What is the proper way of setting this onClick Listener?</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> I have to set it in this adapter class, not the main class for my own reasons. </p> <p>You shuldn't implement a listener inside the <code>getView()</code> unless you what set a listener on a particular view inside your row layout.</p>
